column5: Hey all...my girlfriend found this video and just had to show it too me... Thought I would share.  http://www.maniacworld.com/twin-baby-moose-in-sprinkler.html

My parents had a big bull last fall rub up against the side of their sunroom, lol.  My oldman feeds turkey in the backyard all the time.  A bear tore down the bird feeder last week, and there was also a monster doe in the backyard a few days ago.  This fall should be a lot of fun!!!  (All this up in Coldwater I might add)
Geez, every creature on earth loves to run through the sprinkler eh  Great video, thanks for sharing that.  Joey
I'm not much on the small children pics and vids, but that was just too cute!!!  Ya gotta love the baby animulz!!!  Thanks a bunch for postng that!!!
That is a cool video brkygetr    Joyfull little calves  Thanks for sharing Leechman

Very cool video, but for some reason an image of Marisa Tomei popped into my head when I watched it   :  (substitute "deer" for moose and "brook" for sprinkler)  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ba7QvrreqU4
LOL.. that was pretty cute.....  by the way Monique got her first moose tag yesterday!
Great vid!  Dippy song....  LOL HD
yeah forgot to mention the less-then-groovy audio.. figured the cinematography would hold its own
